headline: Kraft Mac & Cheese and PopUp Bagels Team up to Drop a New Limited-Edition Schmear
summary: PITTSBURGH & CHICAGO, October 01, 2025--Kraft Mac & Cheese and Not Famous but Known® PopUp Bagels are teaming up to bring fans an all-new, limited-edition "Kraft Mac & Cream Cheese" schmear. Available at all PopUp Bagels stores from October 9 to October 15, the mac & cheese-flavored schmear brings the famous flavor of Kraft Mac & Cheese to fans’ breakfast bagel run via the signature "grip, rip and dip" PopUp Bagels experience.
